### Get all messages with default pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/all
Accept: application/json

### Get all messages with custom pagination (first page, 5 items)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/all?page=0&size=5
Accept: application/json

### Get all messages with custom pagination (second page, 10 items)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/all?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get messages by chat ID with default pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byChatId/-1001125352795
Accept: application/json

### Get messages by chat ID with custom pagination (first page, 5 items)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byChatId/123456789?page=0&size=5
Accept: application/json

### Get messages by chat ID with custom pagination (second page, 10 items)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byChatId/123456789?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get messages by another chat ID
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byChatId/987654321?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get message by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byId/555555555
Accept: application/json

### Get message by ID (example 2)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byId/777777777
Accept: application/json

### Get message by ID (not found case)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byId/999999999
Accept: application/json

### Get messages where chatId and senderId are the same (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byChatIdAndSenderId/-1001281542836
Accept: application/json

### Get messages where chatId and senderId are the same (custom pagination, first page)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byChatIdAndSenderId/123456789?page=0&size=5
Accept: application/json

### Get messages where chatId and senderId are the same (custom pagination, second page)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byChatIdAndSenderId/123456789?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get messages where chatId and senderId are the same (example with channel ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byChatIdAndSenderId/-1001125352795?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get messages where chatId and senderId are the same (not found case)
GET http://localhost:8080/messages/byChatIdAndSenderId/999999999
Accept: application/json